WEBVTT

00:00.136 --> 00:01.307
<i>Previously on Boston Legal</i>

00:01.307 --> 00:02.262
Nice night.

00:02.297 --> 00:03.217
Suddenly it is.

00:03.218 --> 00:04.804
You had sex with her here?

00:04.839 --> 00:08.578
Hot, sweaty sex…

00:08.613 --> 00:10.335
in the coat check room.

00:10.370 --> 00:11.855
I'm not a one-woman man.

00:11.890 --> 00:13.341
As long as we're together,

00:13.341 --> 00:16.065
feel free to have sex
with anyone else you want.

00:16.065 --> 00:18.721
I care about what could happen
to this firm now!

00:18.721 --> 00:21.569
Let me tell you what will happen
to this firm if Denny Crane left.

00:21.569 --> 00:23.113
It would dry up and blow away
and you with it!

00:23.113 --> 00:24.854
By the way, did I tell you?

00:24.889 --> 00:27.410
Bev and I are getting married.

00:27.445 --> 00:29.931
No. I would have remembered that.

